// TEST: hot_reload_state
// CATEGORY: integration
// DESCRIPTION: State persistence across hot-reloads (counter increments)
// EXPECT: success
// ASSERT: (counter increments across reloads - manual verification needed)
//
// Demonstrates:
// - Mutable global state
// - _process() lifecycle hook
// - Variable increment
// - State persistence during hot-reload
//
// TESTING HOT-RELOAD:
// 1. Attach to Node2D and run scene
// 2. Counter increments every frame
// 3. Modify this file (e.g., change increment to +2)
// 4. Save file
// 5. Counter continues from last value (not reset to 0)
//
